BBEX3.M.TMT.USD.CA.AC.A01: Exchange rates for the US dollar in Turkmenistan / USD 1 = TMT ... (middle)
General: Currency conversion with effect from 1 January 2009 at the rate of TMM 5,000 = TMT 1; for exchange rates until 2008, see BBEX3:M:TMM:USD:CA:AC:A01. The manat is pegged to the US dollar.
Source: Central Bank of Turkmenistan, Ashgabat.
Comment on 2009-01: Currency conversion with effect from 1 January 2009 at the rate of TMM 5,000 = TMT 1.

Comment on 2015-01: With effect from 1 January 2015, the fixed exchange rate between the Turkmen manat and the US dollar of USD 1 = TMT 2.85 was changed to USD 1 = TMT 3.50; this corresponds to a depreciation of the Turkmen manat vis-á-vis the US dollar of 18.6%.
